=Episode 11=

23
00:02:00,200 --> 00:02:01,440
Sudah lama aku tidak makan daging.

24
00:02:02,920 --> 00:02:03,840
Mendengarmu berkata begitu…

25
00:02:04,000 --> 00:02:05,560
Aku juga jadi ingin makan daging.

26
00:02:06,040 --> 00:02:07,040
Benar, kan?

27
00:02:08,160 --> 00:02:09,200
Aku merindukan…

28
00:02:09,440 --> 00:02:10,800
hotpot, nasi, dan sup ayam.

29
00:02:11,480 --> 00:02:13,880
Aku ingin makan Ayam Kungpao,

30
00:02:14,200 --> 00:02:15,200
semur daging…

31
00:02:15,320 --> 00:02:16,440
dan juga daging merah rebus.

32
00:02:17,280 --> 00:02:17,960
Sudahlah…

33
00:02:18,480 --> 00:02:19,200
Jangan bicara lagi.

34
00:02:19,720 --> 00:02:20,560
Aku sudah lapar.

35
00:02:23,000 --> 00:02:23,800
Baginda.

36
00:02:24,000 --> 00:02:25,520
Aku carikan makanan untuk Anda.

37
00:02:27,400 --> 00:02:28,000
Mengmeng.

38
00:02:28,680 --> 00:02:29,320
Tunggu.

39
00:02:40,000 --> 00:02:40,880
Chang kong.

40
00:02:42,840 --> 00:02:44,680
Chang Kong, kau hebat sekali!

41
00:03:11,880 --> 00:03:12,360
Ini.

42
00:03:14,560 --> 00:03:15,520
Terima kasih.

43
00:03:33,480 --> 00:03:34,480
Di bukit tandus…

44
00:03:36,560 --> 00:03:38,840
Di bukit tandus
masih pilih-pilih makanan.

45
00:03:39,360 --> 00:03:40,880
Bukankah sama saja setelah masuk mulut?

46
00:03:41,960 --> 00:03:43,400
Orang seperti kalian…

47
00:03:47,160 --> 00:03:48,080
sudahlah.

48
00:03:48,960 --> 00:03:50,680
Kami yang dari keluarga kerajaan,

49
00:03:50,880 --> 00:03:53,480
selalu harus tampak anggun
meski sedang di luar.

50
00:03:53,800 --> 00:03:54,800
Elegan.

51
00:03:55,120 --> 00:03:56,280
Sopan.

52
00:03:57,720 --> 00:03:59,120
Berbeda dengan kalian.

53
00:04:08,840 --> 00:04:09,760
Mengmeng.

54
00:04:09,920 --> 00:04:10,920
Terima kasih.

55
00:04:11,280 --> 00:04:13,240
Xiao Ai, makanlah, ayo.

56
00:04:13,440 --> 00:04:14,440
Terima kasih, Putri.

57
00:04:20,080 --> 00:04:20,720
Terima kasih.

58
00:04:24,680 --> 00:04:25,560
Coba katakan.

59
00:04:25,760 --> 00:04:27,160
Sekarang kita bisa makan daging,

60
00:04:27,920 --> 00:04:29,240
bukankah enak kalau ada arak?

61
00:04:30,320 --> 00:04:31,200
Benar.

62
00:04:31,480 --> 00:04:33,000
Sudah lama tidak minum arak.

63
00:04:35,320 --> 00:04:36,400
Mengmeng, untukmu.

64
00:04:36,960 --> 00:04:37,640
Terima kasih.

65
00:04:38,680 --> 00:04:39,760
Murong Chen?

66
00:04:40,320 --> 00:04:43,000
Kenapa di tubuhmu bisa ada
barang sebanyak itu?

67
00:04:46,960 --> 00:04:48,120
- Untuk Xiao Ai.
- Terima kasih.

68
00:04:50,560 --> 00:04:51,880
Kau bisa sulap?

69
00:04:55,680 --> 00:04:56,640
- Untuk Chang Kong.
- Terima kasih, Baginda.

70
00:04:57,880 --> 00:04:59,040
Mana punyaku?

71
00:04:59,960 --> 00:05:01,440
Ada, sebentar.

72
00:05:02,600 --> 00:05:03,520
Masih ada?

73
00:05:08,480 --> 00:05:09,880
Chang Kong, di dalam buntalan.

74
00:05:13,720 --> 00:05:14,760
Cepat…

75
00:05:15,040 --> 00:05:16,160
Mari kita bersulang.

76
00:05:18,000 --> 00:05:19,560
Bersulang?

77
00:05:20,360 --> 00:05:21,520
Seperti ini.

78
00:05:23,960 --> 00:05:24,840
Bersulang.

79
00:05:25,440 --> 00:05:26,880
Bersulang!

80
00:05:33,560 --> 00:05:34,320
Aku…

81
00:05:34,840 --> 00:05:36,480
tokoh utama, Jiang Mengmeng.

82
00:05:36,680 --> 00:05:38,320
Putri Kesembilan Kerajaan Ruo Shui.

83
00:05:38,480 --> 00:05:40,120
Pintar dan cantik.

84
00:05:41,280 --> 00:05:43,400
Jika digambarkan dengan satu kata…

85
00:05:43,560 --> 00:05:44,560
kau tahu apa itu?

86
00:05:45,000 --> 00:05:46,200
Sempurna!

87
00:05:46,360 --> 00:05:49,320
Bisa bertemu denganku,
berarti diberkati selama tiga generasi.

88
00:05:52,120 --> 00:05:54,120
Diberkati selama tiga generasi?

89
00:05:55,320 --> 00:05:56,360
Salah.

90
00:05:57,760 --> 00:06:03,040
Aku yang diberkati tiga generasi
karena bertemu kalian.

91
00:06:08,520 --> 00:06:09,640
Selama ini…

92
00:06:13,440 --> 00:06:14,720
semua karena kalian…

93
00:06:15,960 --> 00:06:16,960
berada di sisiku,

94
00:06:18,680 --> 00:06:19,480
melindungiku,

95
00:06:19,760 --> 00:06:20,440
menemaniku.

96
00:06:21,400 --> 00:06:22,480
Tanpa kalian,

97
00:06:22,640 --> 00:06:24,760
kesulitan ini pasti sukar dilalui.

98
00:06:25,040 --> 00:06:27,240
Sebenarnya aku kemari
untuk mencari cinta sejati.

99
00:06:28,120 --> 00:06:31,680
Tapi kalian adalah teman Jiang Mengmeng…

100
00:06:32,200 --> 00:06:36,600
yang teramat sangat penting.

101
00:06:37,200 --> 00:06:40,160
Tak peduli kelak akan menghadapi apa,

102
00:06:40,480 --> 00:06:42,960
atau masa depan akan seperti apa,

103
00:06:44,040 --> 00:06:45,360
aku tidak akan lupa.

104
00:06:45,680 --> 00:06:49,200
Kita makan daging
dan minum arak bersama.

105
00:06:49,560 --> 00:06:51,160
Berkelana di dunia bersama.

106
00:06:51,400 --> 00:06:53,200
Saling setia dan tulus.

107
00:06:53,560 --> 00:06:54,400
Xiao Ai.

108
00:06:54,760 --> 00:06:55,800
Putri.

109
00:06:56,320 --> 00:06:58,200
Kau baik hati dan juga manis.

110
00:06:58,360 --> 00:06:59,240
Chang Kong,

111
00:06:59,400 --> 00:07:01,280
kau jarang bicara,

112
00:07:01,440 --> 00:07:03,520
tapi, kau tegas dan kalem,

113
00:07:04,400 --> 00:07:05,640
memberikan rasa aman.

114
00:07:07,160 --> 00:07:08,280
Terima kasih, Putri Kesembilan.

115
00:07:08,560 --> 00:07:09,440
Song Che.

116
00:07:09,560 --> 00:07:10,240
Hadir!

117
00:07:10,760 --> 00:07:13,280
Otakmu terkadang bodoh.

118
00:07:13,480 --> 00:07:14,320
Kaku dan terlalu lempeng.

119
00:07:14,480 --> 00:07:17,800
Suka terburu-buru dan
gegabah dalam bertindak,

120
00:07:17,960 --> 00:07:19,120
tidak peduli konsekuensi.

121
00:07:20,160 --> 00:07:21,040
Tapi…

122
00:07:21,200 --> 00:07:22,200
tapi…

123
00:07:23,400 --> 00:07:26,360
kau selalu memimpin di garis depan kami.

124
00:07:26,560 --> 00:07:30,680
Kau jenderal kami yang gagah berani.

125
00:07:36,320 --> 00:07:37,200
Mengmeng.

126
00:07:37,880 --> 00:07:38,680
Mengmeng.

127
00:07:39,360 --> 00:07:40,320
Bagaimana denganku?

128
00:07:41,160 --> 00:07:42,600
Murong Chen.

129
00:07:42,920 --> 00:07:44,040
Murong Chen, kau…

130
00:07:44,920 --> 00:07:45,840
kau…

131
00:07:49,560 --> 00:07:51,520
Kubawa dia pergi muntah dulu.

132
00:07:53,760 --> 00:07:55,080
Kenapa kau minum sebanyak itu?

133
00:07:56,560 --> 00:07:58,320
Cepatlah kembali.

134
00:08:07,960 --> 00:08:09,640
Kuceritakan sebuah rahasia padamu.

135
00:08:10,400 --> 00:08:13,520
Tapi, jangan beri tahu Murong Chen.

136
00:08:14,560 --> 00:08:16,480
Sepertinya kau benar-benar sudah mabuk.

137
00:08:18,960 --> 00:08:22,880
Saat kukira dia akan meninggal,

138
00:08:23,600 --> 00:08:27,600
aku berjanji untuk memberikannya
kenangan indah untuk terakhir kalinya.

139
00:08:30,000 --> 00:08:32,480
Sejak itu,
setiap kali tatapan kami bertemu,

140
00:08:34,000 --> 00:08:36,520
aku akan merasa tidak nyaman.

141
00:08:38,600 --> 00:08:39,640
Bukankah kau bilang…

142
00:08:40,160 --> 00:08:41,520
anggap saja seperti mimpi?

143
00:08:41,680 --> 00:08:42,920
Tinggal dilupakan saja, kan?

144
00:08:43,480 --> 00:08:44,960
Aku memang berkata begitu.

145
00:08:46,880 --> 00:08:48,400
Tapi, aku tahu…

146
00:08:49,880 --> 00:08:52,280
kami sudah tidak bisa
kembali ke hubungan yang dulu lagi.

147
00:08:53,640 --> 00:08:55,520
Tak peduli seberapa keras aku ingin…

148
00:08:55,920 --> 00:08:58,800
ingin berpura-pura terlihat tak peduli,

149
00:09:01,280 --> 00:09:04,160
tapi tanpa sadar aku akan teringat…

150
00:09:07,440 --> 00:09:09,520
pernyataan cinta darinya
yang sungguh-sungguh saat itu,

151
00:09:10,640 --> 00:09:11,760
dan pernyataan cintaku yang palsu,

152
00:09:15,520 --> 00:09:19,280
lalu ciuman itu.

153
00:09:20,600 --> 00:09:22,640
Padahal aku sudah punya Yun Ya.

154
00:09:23,400 --> 00:09:26,600
Tidak seharusnya menganggap
Murong Chen layaknya seorang pria.

155
00:09:31,720 --> 00:09:32,560
Sebenarnya…

156
00:09:34,560 --> 00:09:37,760
kau tak perlu bingung
antara Murong Chen dan Yun Ya.

157
00:09:48,680 --> 00:09:49,680
Sudahlah.

158
00:09:51,360 --> 00:09:53,200
Mungkin aku terlalu memaksamu.

159
00:09:55,440 --> 00:09:57,520
Seharusnya aku memberimu sedikit waktu.

160
00:09:58,800 --> 00:10:00,360
Membiarkanku berpikir dengan baik.

161
00:10:02,040 --> 00:10:03,240
Berpikir hingga jelas,

162
00:10:04,520 --> 00:10:07,840
apa yang hatimu inginkan.

163
00:10:10,880 --> 00:10:11,880
Xiao Meng.

164
00:10:14,160 --> 00:10:15,120
Aku sungguh berharap…

165
00:10:16,400 --> 00:10:18,480
bisa seumur hidup seperti ini denganmu.

166
00:10:41,080 --> 00:10:42,560
Kalian pikir kalian bisa lari?

167
00:10:54,400 --> 00:10:55,080
Kakak Seperguruan,

168
00:10:55,280 --> 00:10:56,120
(Yun Zong)
biar kami yang tangani di sini.

169
00:10:56,280 --> 00:10:57,240
Kalian pergi dulu.

170
00:10:58,720 --> 00:10:59,680
Cepat pergi.

171
00:11:07,400 --> 00:11:08,520
Aku mau lihat,

172
00:11:08,720 --> 00:11:10,040
kalian bisa lari sejauh apa.

173
00:11:19,520 --> 00:11:20,840
Kak Mu.

174
00:11:21,040 --> 00:11:22,200
Aku takut.

175
00:11:23,640 --> 00:11:24,600
Jangan takut.

176
00:11:24,880 --> 00:11:26,080
Aku akan melindungimu.

177
00:11:47,560 --> 00:11:48,680
Putri sudah bangun?

178
00:11:50,560 --> 00:11:51,800
Putri baik-baik saja?

179
00:11:52,120 --> 00:11:52,960
Aku tidak apa-apa.

180
00:11:53,160 --> 00:11:54,680
Hanya bermimpi aneh.

181
00:11:56,880 --> 00:11:57,720
Kerjakan urusanmu.

182
00:12:08,800 --> 00:12:09,360
Tunggu.

183
00:12:09,600 --> 00:12:10,960
Kenapa kau menyuruhku kemari?

184
00:12:11,440 --> 00:12:12,120
Aku ingin bertanya.

185
00:12:12,280 --> 00:12:13,280
Saat minum kemarin,

186
00:12:13,480 --> 00:12:14,920
aku tak mengatakan hal yang aneh, kan?

187
00:12:15,480 --> 00:12:16,760
Kemarin kau bicara banyak.

188
00:12:16,920 --> 00:12:18,800
Chang Kong, Xiao Ai, Song Che,
semuanya dengar.

189
00:12:18,920 --> 00:12:19,880
Maksudku bukan itu.

190
00:12:21,040 --> 00:12:22,040
Maksudku…

191
00:12:23,520 --> 00:12:25,360
aku tidak mengatakan padamu…

192
00:12:26,840 --> 00:12:27,960
yang tidak sepantasnya diucapkan, kan?

193
00:12:31,280 --> 00:12:32,160
Ada.

194
00:12:36,400 --> 00:12:37,280
Katamu…

195
00:12:38,760 --> 00:12:43,480
aku adalah orang tertampan
yang kau temui di dunia ini.

196
00:12:43,760 --> 00:12:45,200
Orang yang paling kau sukai.

197
00:12:45,480 --> 00:12:47,480
Lalu, kau sangat menyesal
sudah membatalkan pertunangan.

198
00:12:49,320 --> 00:12:51,000
Kau ingin menikah denganku di situ juga,

199
00:12:51,560 --> 00:12:53,840
lalu meminta Song Che
menjadi mak comblang kita.

200
00:12:54,080 --> 00:12:55,280
Aku sudah setuju.

201
00:12:56,160 --> 00:12:57,280
Menyenangkan?

202
00:12:58,320 --> 00:12:59,360
Tidak.

203
00:13:00,800 --> 00:13:02,760
Untung aku tak mengatakan
hal-hal yang aneh.

204
00:13:03,760 --> 00:13:05,160
Apa yang kau pakai di kepalamu itu?

205
00:13:05,360 --> 00:13:07,080
Terlihat bodoh dan jelek sekali.

206
00:13:10,080 --> 00:13:11,480
Jelekkah? Akan kuganti yang lain.

207
00:13:11,880 --> 00:13:12,720
Tunggu aku.

208
00:13:17,120 --> 00:13:18,560
Masih seperti dia yang dulu.

209
00:13:19,400 --> 00:13:21,800
Untuk apa juga aku dibuat resah
olehnya sebelum ini?

210
00:13:23,840 --> 00:13:24,680
Jiang Mengmeng.

211
00:13:24,960 --> 00:13:25,760
Kau hanya melakukan kesalahan…

212
00:13:25,840 --> 00:13:27,640
yang bisa dilakukan wanita manapun
di dunia ini.

213
00:13:28,400 --> 00:13:29,600
Tidak masalah terpesona sesaat.

214
00:13:30,080 --> 00:13:32,000
Asalkan posisi pria utama tak berubah,

215
00:13:32,880 --> 00:13:34,360
bertahan adalah kemenangan.

216
00:13:36,360 --> 00:13:37,120
Semangat!

217
00:13:43,200 --> 00:13:44,520
Pria utama?

218
00:13:46,360 --> 00:13:48,520
Apa yang dimaksud Mengmeng itu aku?

219
00:13:50,760 --> 00:13:51,720
Aku sudah tahu.

220
00:13:51,840 --> 00:13:53,760
Murong Chen bukanlah lawanku.

221
00:13:58,040 --> 00:13:59,680
(Kabupaten He Zhao ke Liang Cheng)

222
00:14:11,360 --> 00:14:14,040
(Liang Cheng)

223
00:14:18,000 --> 00:14:19,040
Di sinilah Liang Cheng.

224
00:14:19,600 --> 00:14:20,600
Liang Cheng?

225
00:14:23,200 --> 00:14:26,320
Di sini tampaknya tidak terlalu makmur.

226
00:14:26,600 --> 00:14:28,840
Tapi, orang yang berlalu lalang
dan pedagangnya…

227
00:14:29,080 --> 00:14:30,520
tampaknya sangat kaya.

228
00:14:33,080 --> 00:14:34,000
Liang Cheng ini…

229
00:14:34,160 --> 00:14:35,760
meski kondisi alamnya sangat buruk,

230
00:14:35,960 --> 00:14:37,520
tapi letak geografisnya sangat bagus.

231
00:14:37,840 --> 00:14:38,920
Utara berbatasan dengan Bei Mo,

232
00:14:39,320 --> 00:14:40,520
selatan berbatasan dengan Nan Cang,

233
00:14:40,720 --> 00:14:41,680
barat berbatasan dengan Ruo Shui,

234
00:14:41,880 --> 00:14:42,800
timur berbatasan dengan Cang Yun.

235
00:14:43,640 --> 00:14:45,400
Pedagang dari banyak kerajaan
dan wilayah…

236
00:14:45,640 --> 00:14:47,200
selalu melewati jalan ini,

237
00:14:47,360 --> 00:14:49,520
maka terjadilah fenomena aneh…

238
00:14:49,760 --> 00:14:51,360
di mana orang kaya terlihat
di daerah miskin.

239
00:14:51,800 --> 00:14:53,000
Orang yang sering bertempur
di luar sepanjang waktu memang hebat.

240
00:14:53,200 --> 00:14:54,280
Jenderal Muda Song.

241
00:14:54,800 --> 00:14:55,720
Nilai geografi sempurna.

242
00:15:15,240 --> 00:15:16,560
Hei, Mu…

243
00:15:18,040 --> 00:15:19,160
cepatlah menangis.

244
00:15:20,880 --> 00:15:22,360
Aku tidak bisa menangis.

245
00:15:22,920 --> 00:15:24,640
Kita tidak akan mendapatkan
sedekah kalau tidak menangis.

246
00:15:24,880 --> 00:15:27,080
Kau ingin Paman Ketujuh
ikut mati kelaparan dengan kita?

247
00:15:47,080 --> 00:15:47,760
Mu bodoh.

248
00:15:47,920 --> 00:15:49,000
